result.name: Budaoweng Hot Pot Restaurant

reviews.text: Very good hot pot, nice view near the window. Good quality ingredients.

I don't like it. It's the worst hotpot I've ever eaten. Service is a basic service and the taste is terrible. It's not a place to pay a small amount of money, but the taste and service are really the worst compared to the cost. I'll tell the people around me not to go.

Apparently this is a very happening place especially during dinner hours. It has a very high class feel andnof course comes with a price too😁. 
Despite the expensive menus,one can be rest assured it's value for money s they serves wide varieties of delicious fresh food here with tip top services from the restaurant staffs.
Aside from their wide varieties of delicious food,it is located on a prime high level inside iSquare with panaromic sea views whereby one can relax with fireworks and laser displays nightly over a romatic dinner within the restaurant. 
Just want to remind all that early reservation is highly recommended as the place is popular among the tourists as well s the locals here.

A medium price Chinese restaurant in the upper floor of Isquare.  I visited this restaurant twice on Saturday.  Advance booking was preferred but not a must.  Window side table not guaranteed.  The harbour view was very attractive, even for local residents.  Choice of dim sum for lunch was not much but still acceptable.  Sushi and hot pot were available.  Sweet soup would be given free upon checking the bill.  Overall service was good.
Good location in TST tourist area right out the MTR station. Great harbour view and of course food is good. Pricy but with good reasons 😅

result.adr_address: 香港尖沙咀彌敦道63號
result.name: 不倒翁中日火鍋料理

reviews.text: 很新鮮的火鍋🍲
這裡雖然是火鍋料理，但中午亦有點心供應，由於位處K11，交通極之方便。這裡地方寬趟舒適，觀境甚佳，維港就在面前。此處點心種類不多，但普遍亦及水準，而此處亦有日式魚生供應，惟因本人對魚生不感興趣，故並無嘗試。這裡中午飲茶不時有點心送贈，另埋單時亦會送贈糖水，雖是免費但絕不欺場。
用餐環境舒適又有無敵大景 午市飲茶套餐價格實惠值得一試
